HEADWORD: Throstling
<hw>Thros"tling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Throttle</er>.]</ety> <def>A disease of bovine cattle, consisting of
a swelling under the throat, which, unless checked, causes
strangulation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Throttle</ent>⟦br⟧
